              basis of fair market value without reference to the tax credit provided for under the
                Income Tax Act or the Income Tax Act (Canada);

that share transactions under paragraph (h) may be governed
              by limits set out in the plan if those limits are based on a reasonable test of
              ability to pay;

except if the administrator has made an order under section 40 (5)
                (c), the sum of the shareholder's aggregate entitlements in respect of
              all tax credit certificates applied for in the year is $2 000 or less, and

